OL,3,CThief who distracted victims to steal
OL,4,Cphones jailed for crime spree
OL,6,FA woman who carried out a spate of
OL,7,Fthefts across four counties has been
OL,8,Fjailed for eight months.
OL,10,FNirix Stanescu, 24, of no fixed abode,
OL,11,Fused distraction techniques to steal
OL,12,Fmobile phones from her victims.
OL,14,FThe offences took place in Surrey,
OL,15,FOxfordshire, Buckinghamshire and
OL,16,FBerkshire.
OL,18,FFour of the offences occurred in
OL,19,FStaines-upon-Thames, Walton-on-Thames
OL,20,Fand Woking.
