OL,3,CThief who distracted victims to steal
OL,4,Cphones jailed for crime spree
OL,6,FFive further offences occurred in
OL,7,FMilton Keynes, Reading, Slough,
OL,8,FWokingham and Oxford.
OL,10,FBetween 4 May 2024 and 12 July 2024,
OL,11,FStanescu entered restaurants in
OL,12,Fvarious locations, approaching people
OL,13,Feating meals and who had their phones
OL,14,Fon tables.
OL,16,FStanescu would place a map or other
OL,17,Fpaperwork over the phone, before
OL,18,Fdistracting her victims and stealing
OL,19,Fthe phone.
