OL,4,Cphones jailed for crime spree
OL,6,FShe was arrested on 25 September and
OL,7,Fcharged the following day.
OL,9,FStanescu pleaded guilty to nine counts
OL,10,Fof theft, each relating to distraction
OL,11,Fthefts of mobile phones.
OL,13,FAt Reading Magistrates' Court on
OL,14,FFriday 27 September, Stanescu was
OL,15,Fsentenced to a total of eight months'
OL,16,Fimprisonment.
