OL,6,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,7,FConstable Michael Hanson, of the
OL,8,FReading Priority Crime Team, said:
OL,9,F"Stanescu would use distracting
OL,10,Ftechniques to target her victims,
OL,11,Fstealing their phones when she
OL,12,Femployed these tactics.
OL,14,F"I am pleased that she pleaded guilty
OL,15,Fat the first hearing and has now been
OL,16,Fsentenced to prison as a result.
OL,18,F"I hope that her time in prison is
OL,19,Fused constructively to reflect on her
OL,20,Foffending behaviour.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
