OL,4,Cphones jailed for crime spree
OL,6,F"Although Stanescu used distractive
OL,7,Ftechniques, this case is a timely
OL,8,Freminder of the risks involved in
OL,9,Fleaving property in full view.
OL,11,F"I would advise people to keep their
OL,12,Fproperty close at hand, or out of
OL,13,Fsight, in order to prevent
OL,14,Fopportunists such as Stanescu
OL,15,Ftargeting them."
