OL,6,FInspector Chris Thoday, from the North
OL,7,FSurrey Neighbourhood Policing
OL,8,FInvestigation Team, said: "We worked
OL,9,Fclosely with Thames Valley Police to
OL,10,Fensure Stanescu was held accountable
OL,11,Ffor her repeated and targeted
OL,12,Foffending that stretched across
OL,13,Fmultiple counties.
OL,15,F"By reviewing CCTV footage and
OL,16,Finterviewing witnesses, we identified
OL,17,FStanescu and her tactics for stealing
OL,18,Fmobile phones.
